thread.title: Cher joins Sydney's Gay and Lesbian Mardi Gras Parade

title: Cher joins Sydney's Gay and Lesbian Mardi Gras Parade
text:
Cher joins Sydney's Gay and Lesbian Mardi Gras Parade   02:13 
Scores of people turn out in Sydney to take part in the Gay and Lesbian Mardi Gras parade with one group, the 39'ers, recognized for the work they've done since the start and Cher in town to celebrate. Francis Maguire
